So thank you.

00:06:15.970 --> 00:06:17.880
And thank you also
to the Kluge Center.

00:06:17.880 --> 00:06:23.010
All of the fellows, the staff,
really made it a really kind

00:06:23.010 --> 00:06:26.120
of a once-in-a-lifetime experience.

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:31.040
So and also, you know, we've
